{"type": "article", "id": 22396, "title": "如果你爱穿男友风牛仔裤，这里有些搭配常识", "description": "当然，如果你有美腿一双，爱穿啥穿啥，你开心就好。", "date": "2016-02-18T10:00:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23521, "name": "Boyfriend jeans"}], "category": 19, "author": 403280, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 201, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153107eyap7xc6Q2biDGkg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">“拿男友的衣服来穿”这件事，上至衬衫夹克，下至牛仔裤，都已经不是什么新鲜的时髦人指南了。自从当年的汤嫂 Katie Holmes 穿着阿汤哥的牛仔裤出门，掐指一算 8 年过去，Boyfriend Jeans 已经变成酷女孩几乎人手一条的经典单品了。</p>\n<p class=\"\">随性、慵懒、一年四季都适用，那也要好好搭配，扬长避短。</p>\n<h2>把衣服塞进裤子里不再是小学生的专利啦</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153100QYPL0ezfwrio8cs5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54264706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.likefreshlaundry.com/dressing-fourth/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Like fresh laundry</a>、<a href=\"http://www.stylepinner.com/street-style-jeans/c3RyZWV0LXN0eWxlLWplYW5z/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Stylepinner</a>、 <a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/style/how-to-style-boyfriend-jeans-in-a-grown-up-way/\">Telegraph</a></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Boyfriend Jeans 宽松随性，但也多为低腰款，虽然能遮肉，但是裤腿肥大。如果你自认不是比例好的长腿星人，就乖乖把衣服塞进裤子里去吧，这个法则适用于衬衫、短袖 T、高领毛衣。不仅是显腿长的问题，整体 look 看起来也会更精神。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021531014e17fnyCb2ixLwBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.fashioninspo.com/street-fashion/best-street-style-looks-from-milan-fashion-week/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Fashion Inspo</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">春夏搭露胃装会是一个不错的选择，前提是你没有小肚腩。</p>\n<h2>真正的勇士敢于直面卷裤脚的寒冷</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153101YRi1WapB0uoVGE5b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://streetstyle.allwomenstalk.com/street-style-ways-to-wear-boyfriend-jeans/6\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">allwomenstalk</a>、<a href=\"http://en.louloumagazine.com/street-style/street-style-mom-et-boyfriend-jeans/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LOULOU</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“腿不够长，卷裤脚来凑”</p>\n<p class=\"\">从对比图可以看出，露出一截脚脖子在视觉上感觉更舒服，扬长避短。卷裤脚也更适合直筒牛仔裤在版型上的发挥。</p>\n<p class=\"\">如果是冬天，可以选择左图的搭配（浅口鞋+中筒袜）保护好自己的脚踝。</p>\n<h2>把你好看的脚背露出来</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021531025MKOkHrBs8SITLNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://justthedesign.tumblr.com/post/114211651048/arielle-nachami-is-wearing-skinny-boyfriend-jeans-from\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Just the design</a>、<a href=\"http://www.whoknowsfashion.com/2014/04/04/wkfs-fashion-friday-take-slouch-in-the-boyfriend-jeans/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Who Knows Fashion</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">除了万年不出错的小白鞋之外，街拍中最常和 Boyfriend jeans 一起出现的，就是高跟鞋。高跟鞋可以挽救松垮牛仔裤带来的腿长劣势，拉长下半身的比例。但是呢，记得一定要大面积地露出脚背。</p>\n<p class=\"\">像右图大表姐这样用靴子塞得满满当当是不是就不如左图 Arielle Nachami 来得清爽？</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153104HZ4Sk3BmRga1VEdF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43376623\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://justthedesign.tumblr.com/post/122091143583/another-classic-boyfriend-jeans-look-white-tee-jeans\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Just the design</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">可以选择的搭配有尖头高跟鞋、玛丽珍鞋或是一字鞋。露出脚背可以防止下半身太过沉闷。</p>\n<h2>啊，你会需要一条丝巾</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153105Qp3qtAXZbkhL6sog.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.60220994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153105PVkUxT9GfaoDjR4p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.6016129\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/style/how-to-style-boyfriend-jeans-in-a-grown-up-way/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Telegraph</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Boyfriend jeans 腰身通常很低，差不多在胯部的位置，因此如果配普通的皮带，常常会在后腰的地方拱起来，不好看。一条丝巾就可以完美解决这个问题，还够特别。</p>\n<p class=\"\">事实上，配饰很重要，如果你全身的单品都走简洁风没什么心机，那么一款特别的包袋、首饰或是丝巾会很加分。</p>\n<h2>至于上装，丰俭由人</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021531066WlDKbNLo3txsXc5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.thefashionspot.com/style-trends/613743-how-to-wear-boyfriend-jeans/#/slide/1\">The Fashion Spot</a></p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">\n\nBoyfriend jeans 的最大特质就在于，无论上装搭配得多么繁复，搭上一条牛仔裤就能瞬间变得简洁。 \n</p>\n<p class=\"\">上装的选择实际上没什么局限性，最简单的单品，比如白色 T 恤、条纹衫、西装上衣、印花衬衫都不太会出错，如果想要出彩，可以试试和牛仔裤同色系的牛仔上衣，或者对比感更强的皮衣。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153107YQwrK1oqWARCMJTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47204969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">  图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.thefashionspot.com/style-trends/613743-how-to-wear-boyfriend-jeans/#/slide/1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Fashion Spot</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自<a href=\"http://themirroronthewall.com/spring-fashion-trend-stripes/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The mirror on the wall</a></p>\n\n"}